subtitleNullable: TFrecords of Mckinsey666's anime faces dataset
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset contains the TFrecords of [Mckinsey666](https://github.com/Mckinsey666/Anime-Face-Dataset)'s anime faces dataset. 


### Content

There are roughly 64,000 anime faces with an image size of 64x64.

![](https://www.googleapis.com/download/storage/v1/b/kaggle-user-content/o/inbox%2F5570735%2Fc9d62165af595ffc511ff783d8f74932%2Ftest2.jpg?generation=1610583751184651&alt=media)




### Acknowledgements

Thanks to [Mckinsey666](https://github.com/Mckinsey666/Anime-Face-Dataset) for the original dataset.
Thanks to [splcher](https://www.kaggle.com/splcher) for sharing these images as a Kaggle Dataset.


### Inspiration

I have been looking into GAN's, and worked with landscapes and paintings. I wanted to apply what I learnt building that model and it apply it do a different typeof image data.
